{"type": "article", "id": 2773, "title": "将茶叶和日历合二为一的茶日历", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-11T07:50:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232536LlkwF5Dmn6vuY7cQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自德国汉堡的工业设计团队 Kolle Rebbe 为德国茶叶品牌 Halssen &amp; Lyon 设计了世界上第一款将茶叶和日历合二为一的作品，让你一年 365 天每天都能品茗不同口味的香浓热茶。这款手工制成的“茶日历”采用被压制成的速溶茶叶薄片，在其表面印上了日期，然后依照日期在茶盒中排好，一本茶日历便大功告成。用户只需轻轻撕掉写着昨日日期的茶叶薄片，然后用热水冲泡，就能用味蕾来感受出时间的流逝，非常诗意。不过由于这款产品手工制作成本极高，目前还未公开发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325338gASoFivXf4m5EqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232533oJlqFGs2kcveDWKR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325342l5Ghz86Ms0yTxQi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232534KbefdJjHmw8yo43r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325345LcKhUHgIv42P1n9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}